rows.label: qst201412_msg0001
rows.name:
Hah... I'm starting to
get a little tired.

rows.label: qst201412_msg0003
rows.name:
But that's exactly when you
have to keep your spirits up!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0004
rows.name:
No one's coming by. Want to chat?
About fashion or something?

rows.label: qst201412_msg0005
rows.name:
Sounds good... I like
pretty accessories.

rows.label: qst201412_msg0006
rows.name:
Wearing them is great, but just
looking at them is fun too.

rows.label: qst201412_msg0007
rows.name: What kind do you like, Zakuro?

rows.label: qst201412_msg0009
rows.name: For me, it's flowers, I guess?

rows.label: qst201412_msg0010
rows.name:
They're pretty and cute, and it's nice
how they're so soothing to look at, right?
And you can wear them in your hair.

rows.label: qst201412_msg0013
rows.name: Huh?! You can call me childish...

rows.label: qst201412_msg0016
rows.name:
...but I like what I
like! I can't help it!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0019
rows.name: In terms of cuteness, I'm the winner!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0020
rows.name: Sounds like sour grapes to me.

rows.label: qst201412_msg0021
rows.name:
And there's no judge! We can't
decide a winner like this!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0023
rows.name:
I'm starting to doubt if this
will ever be settled...
